>  The value must be in the FC3339 format. Example: 2020-06-28T11:33:00.000+08:00. If the parameter is left empty, the file sharing link is permanently valid.', example='2020-06-28T11:33:00.000+08:00'),
  expired?: boolean(name='Expired', description='Specifies whether the file sharing link expires.', example='False'),
